ticket_fields.description: 1 if ticket was assigned through Playlist's Autoplay feature. Otherwise, field is 0 or left blank.
ticket_fields.raw_description: 1 if ticket was assigned through Playlist's Autoplay feature. Otherwise, field is 0 or left blank.

ticket_fields.title: Prevent AutoSolve Expire On
ticket_fields.agent_description: Set the date that the tag from "Prevent AutoSolve" macro will expire on.

ticket_fields.title: Routing Priority
ticket_fields.agent_description: Used to determine order in which to route conversation based on customer attributes

ticket_fields.title: Assignee Geography
ticket_fields.agent_description: The geography of the assignee of the conversation

ticket_fields.title: Customer Geography
ticket_fields.agent_description: Geography of the customer, based on the timezone offset in their browser.

ticket_fields.title: Insights Customer Environment Type
ticket_fields.agent_description: Environment type of customer that ticket is made on behalf of.

ticket_fields.title: Reassigns
ticket_fields.agent_description: Number of times a ticket has been reassigned (caps at 5).

ticket_fields.title: Customer Name
ticket_fields.agent_description: Name of customer that ticket is made on behalf of.
